Class TestModelServlet

java.lang.Object
  HttpServlet
      katrenko.ws.TestModelServlet

public class TestModelServlet
extends HttpServlet

Client for the TestModel web service. To invoke a service make sure that the port number in String endpoint = "http://localhost:8080/axis/services/TestModel"; is set accordingly. Change it if needed.

To run this client, use http://localhost:8080/TestModel/applyModel
